channel.title: Help please with this strangething
channel.description: Hey, i really know nothing to do about this, my problem is, my graphic card program stuff doesnt start and the screen size is 800x600 and it cant be changed, i didnt did anything, i just restarted my laptop and then it happend, its NOT in safe mode. i cant play any games anymore because of this Does anyone know how i can fix this?

item.title: Help please with this strangething
item.dc:creator: @JakeP JakeP
item.description:
@JakeP wrote:

Find your graphics card model and google for any new drivers, usually that fixes the problem. If it is saying “is not working correctly” then it is most likely just the drivers.

It isn’t a hardware issue, you would have no screen at all if that was the case.
